    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Yeah, having hacked [scribe](http://bollwyvl.github.io/scribe/) into the [notebook](https://github.com/bollwyvl/nb-wysiwyg) there is a lot of stuff to be explored, and likely a lot of common patterns that could be reused.\n\nI think for the most part integrating with `cell.code_mirror.on(...)` will be _good enough_, or even the [CM document model](http://codemirror.net/doc/manual.html#api_doc) for fancier things, but i can imagine cases where an evented model on Cell might be necessary.\n"
